# Project Structure Guide

This project is organized as follows:

- The main application code resides in the [app/](mdc:app) directory.
- API endpoints are located in [app/api/](mdc:app/api).
- UI components are in [components/](mdc:components), with shared UI elements in [components/ui/](mdc:components/ui).
- Shared logic and utilities are in [lib/](mdc:lib) and [hooks/](mdc:hooks).
- TypeScript types are defined in [types/](mdc:types) and [draftkings-bet/types/](mdc:draftkings-bet/types).
- Static assets are in [public/](mdc:public).
- Configuration files include [package.json](mdc:package.json), [tsconfig.json](mdc:tsconfig.json), [tailwind.config.ts](mdc:tailwind.config.ts), and [next.config.mjs](mdc:next.config.mjs).
- Environment variables are managed in [.env.local](mdc:.env.local) and [.env.example](mdc:.env.example).

Refer to this guide for high-level navigation of the codebase.
